{"tid":949362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍做香港航空宣傳大使","createTime":"2018-12-20T17:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T11:12:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"45e5f519aecfa59c885062185ab94d3a321cd7d0","tid":949362,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"國際動作巨星成龍獲香港航空公司邀請擔任宣傳大使，宣傳由本月30日開始來往香港與溫哥華的航線，成龍將會乘搭該航線第一班機飛到溫哥華，其荷里活動作喜劇《火拼時速》（Rush Hour）拍檔基斯德加（Chris Tucker）則會於7月1日與成龍一起宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n香港航空公司發言人表示：「我哋好開心可以同成龍合作，一個北美顧客好信任嘅人物，去幫我哋擴展業務去加拿大做首次亮相，希望可以吸引國際觀眾。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.seehua.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/capture-20170611-204710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.seehua.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fcapture-20170611-204710.jpg&h=e8d2c757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170609/photo/bkn-20170609205722386-0609_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170610073540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170609%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170609205722386-0609_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170610073540&h=cc8006a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48394483_10157299351932448_8005977910584279040_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=6ae5e23498fc277761dc13068548b818&amp;oe=5C9B838D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F48394483_10157299351932448_8005977910584279040_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D6ae5e23498fc277761dc13068548b818%26oe%3D5C9B838D&h=0593a18f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4203b14ad79b5547ab352c86180d339c1c70c70","tid":949362,"uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"成龍為香港航空拍攝宣傳片，前日航空公司的Facebook專頁上載拍攝花絮片段。據稱成龍擔任航空公司的形象大使，宣傳於月底開通的往返溫哥華及香港直飛航線。片段中見成龍被空姐們團團包圍，他要飲奶茶又食雞蛋仔，跟空姐們玩自拍，他又在機艙耍功夫，十足活力先生。 片段中成龍講英語，有網民問為何他不講普通話？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成龍曾被冠以「品牌殺手」，過往他代言的部分產品曾出現問題，故又有成龍代言魔咒之說，更有網民在航空公司的Facebook專頁留言：「祝好運！」</span>"},{"pid":"dd3d623e601b1a70cb5821fa1a2dc4d72209b942","tid":949362,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"rip hx"},{"pid":"b3aaf3bc561ed0c902f438224b4e6e807e5b921c","tid":949362,"uid":27664,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T99Hcd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT99Hcd2.png&h=8fd4d063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成虫下面隻手做乜</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f2bf4646af8d68f2f1f7c7020ddd81c403fa10","tid":949362,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"成龍又成功燈死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c777a301d840560eb7ce33dc318bfa336ba46599","tid":949362,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d5d087eeb0da979c0bf4d1259987b2d4ac49b4","tid":949362,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3aaf3bc561ed0c902f438224b4e6e807e5b921c","tid":949362,"uid":27664,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T99Hcd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT99Hcd2.png&h=8fd4d063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成虫下面隻手做乜</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"陳曬四件空雞"},{"pid":"6eaa1e3fa8a656ae2b9a43db6e0821f9efdce09c","tid":949362,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"一個也不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2c6d833ec833daa6e18e942f07c6a5500fd5f5","tid":949362,"uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"第一張左面第一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37158c052b8b9152782b58065f423234ace02adb","tid":949362,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"又中"},{"pid":"32a32ff4ba7af4492079ea35096eaa886a5be835","tid":949362,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大獲"},{"pid":"d86849d3daa4f10a4683d0cdf5f9a5525003d643","tid":949362,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"你係大哥4出1會選?  <br />\n<br />\n選最矮果件<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35afa1e2bcbf32e1f250e634705eca90cf67e07e","tid":949362,"uid":2110,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"希望成龍可以做中國同香港既宣傳大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef31c8cffa9cff6a2ce3d3dd877623bacc86c56","tid":949362,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"用左一年就登死左hx"},{"pid":"8155a29b58a4ec4a192c3777da7deee137e5714d","tid":949362,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7190d0dcf609a31420136353d034539e0cdeb404","tid":949362,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"應該就快唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d384c9dc888c9cda2650c3a05591cb9982399b7","tid":949362,"uid":20867,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2014-08-19/450/20140819001810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2014-08-19%2F450%2F20140819001810.jpg&h=0fd2568c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e1cfccc40ce6b3846412a4cde3d1e2046f6dc1f","tid":949362,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f2bf4646af8d68f2f1f7c7020ddd81c403fa10","tid":949362,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"成龍又成功燈死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"次次代言，間公司都大獲"},{"pid":"5648f5ba5fd4db4f42053aa4b7e57d78bed74dcb","tid":949362,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.popnews.hk/?p=19942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2F%3Fp%3D19942&d=h6C%2F96BWWbDS4raQe2WXETA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=31ee4825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.popnews.hk/?p=19942</a>"},{"pid":"524dfd2587b5141e3162fe6d5cdb18715a7f4718","tid":949362,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"圖1左1+圖2右1雙飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1095269eaac4869337132dceb576b9f51009c61b","tid":949362,"uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"當年小霸王學習機在中國暢銷，雖然有抄襲任天堂之嫌，不過當時知識版權並未普及，所以都無乜所謂。而成龍就成為了他們的代言人，結果公司在2004倒閉。90年代的時候，愛多VCD老板睇中成龍人氣，以450萬高價請得成龍做代言人，令其品牌當時暢銷一時，但過了不久並因為經營不善，多方面欠債，老板則成為階下囚。又係90年代，成龍幫汾煌可樂拍廣告，可惜短短幾年就已經半停產，之後漸漸消失。<br />\n<br />\n成龍最出名的廣告就係霸王洗頭水，不過當年都曾經出現負面新聞而令到股價大跌，雖然最後成功澄清，但聲譽已經受損。講起股價，一間流動網絡商網秦的老闆，曾經講過：「網秦要保護成龍，大家一起做成龍的保鏢」，結果第二日一開市股價就暴跌60%，雖然未必同成龍有直接關係，不過成龍魔做代言人的威力的確不可睇少。成龍曾經為中國Volkswagen開迪做代言人，結果全年在中國只銷售900架，現在亦已經在中國停產。<br />\n<br />\n格力空調曾經在中國得到連續十年全國銷售冠軍，代言人又是成龍，結果之後出現一連串負面新聞，地位被動搖，結果要令到其老總以及現今為首富的王健林一齊拍廣告挽救聲譽。食物品牌成龍大哥都有涉獵，佢曾經為思念食品做代言人，點知在2011年思念水餃就被檢出有菌，要全中國緊急下架。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>還有身為中國禁毒宣傳形象大使的成龍，兒子房祖明卻因為在中國吸毒而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n睇返咁多品牌都發生有大有小的事件，今次香港航空作為航空公司，成龍作為代言人真的很令人擔心。</strong>"},{"pid":"7c627a21e8a45b75c8eec867eb76487065b359e7","tid":949362,"uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"35afa1e2bcbf32e1f250e634705eca90cf67e07e","tid":949362,"uid":2110,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"希望成龍可以做中國同香港既宣傳大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20090421/large/21la2p1new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20090421%2Flarge%2F21la2p1new.jpg&h=735d2416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f951573c7dcec8f47a8108a23e43944b203a3726","tid":949362,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"冇啊冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b7e96071f04f4b936fa9c4c30e54451f9317b3","tid":949362,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"咁就大鑊 港航睇怕避唔到空難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9114383a1ceb9efb27772caf3301abd9be53c277","tid":949362,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"好搵唔搵搵成龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}